charges.charge_description: On or about July 20, 1992 deft did move and travel in interstate travel from Minn. to Illinois and elsewhere with intent to avoid prosecution for violation of probation after conviction for possession of cocaine all in violation of Mn. Statute 609.14 and 152.023 sub 2.

charges.charge_disposition: U. S. Attorney dismissed the complaint against deft. This is an unlawful flight matter. Subject has been arrested in Dalls, Texas, and Hennepin County Sheriff has been notified so as to commence stte extradition proceeding (-1)
